      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IVORY PYGMY (2) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and five placings from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (23.18) when fourth over 400m at this track in a Other. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. COOLER MAC LASS (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (23.21) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Key player if finds best. SHAKA GOES BANG (6) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 6 length 4th at Angle Park (19.96). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. In the mix. REFERENT POWER (8) can sneak into the finish.",
